DEPENDENCIES:
============
Install all the following dependencies

1. http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Lttoolbox
2. http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Installation
3. http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Foma
4. http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/OpenFST
5. Optional http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/SFST
6. Mandatory http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Hfst


INSTALL:
=======
Run make to install

Run "make morphTest" and "make test" to test your installation

TROUBLESHOOT:
============
If you get segmentation fault errors, run "make clean" and run "make" again

OPTIONAL:
========
If you want modes, run "make modes". 
You may remove comp-words.pl and COMPOUNDLIST from modes/*.mode to keep it simple. Also change the paths of perl accordingly.

